gari\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"content.DevanagariRecord\",\"title\":\"devanagari\",\"id\":2777,\"bb\":568237,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/9/30/devanagari/\",\"body_final\":\"अपि चेत्सुदुराचारो भजते मामनन्यभाक् ।\u003cbr/\u003eसाधुरेव स मन्तव्य: सम्यग्व्यवसितो हि स: ॥ ३० ॥\"}]},{\"section\":\"verse_text\",\"section_title\":\"Books.Verse.verse-text\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"content.Record\",\"title\":\"verse_text\",\"id\":2778,\"bb\":2458,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/9/30/b2458/\",\"body_value\":\"\u003cem\u003eapi cet su-durācāro\u003cbr /\u003ebhajate mām ananya-bhāk\u003cbr /\u003esādhur eva sa mantavyaḥ\u003cbr /\u003esamyag vyavasito hi saḥ\u003c/em\u003e\"}]},{\"section\":\"synonyms\",\"section_title\":\"Books.Verse.synonyms\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"books.Synonyms\",\"title\":\"synonyms\",\"id\":2779,\"bb\":2459,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/9/30/b2459/\",\"shadow_value\":\"\u003cem\u003eapi\u003c/em\u003e – even; \u003cem\u003ecet\u003c/em\u003e – if; \u003cem\u003esu-durācāraḥ\u003c/em\u003e – one committing the most abominable actions; \u003cem\u003ebhajate\u003c/em\u003e – is engaged in devotional service; \u003cem\u003emām\u003c/em\u003e – unto Me; \u003cem\u003eananya-bhāk\u003c/em\u003e – without deviation; \u003cem\u003esādhuḥ\u003c/em\u003e – a saint; \u003cem\u003eeva\u003c/em\u003e – certainly; \u003cem\u003esaḥ\u003c/em\u003e – he; \u003cem\u003emantavyaḥ\u003c/em\u003e – is to be considered; \u003cem\u003esamyak\u003c/em\u003e – completely; \u003cem\u003evyavasitaḥ\u003c/em\u003e – situated in determination; \u003cem\u003ehi\u003c/em\u003e – certainly; \u003cem\u003esaḥ\u003c/em\u003e – he.\",\"word_for_word_value\":[{\"word\":\"api\",\"translation\":\"even\"},{\"word\":\"cet\",\"translation\":\"if\"},{\"word\":\"su-durācāraḥ\",\"translation\":\"one committing the most abominable actions\"},{\"word\":\"bhajate\",\"translation\":\"is engaged in devotional service\"},{\"word\":\"mām\",\"translation\":\"unto Me\"},{\"word\":\"ananya-bhāk\",\"t